flowchart TD
    ORDERS["/pos/orders\nOrders list page\nBreadcrumb: POS / Orders / {tab}"]

    ORDERS -->|Default tab: Sales| SALES_TAB["Sales section tabs:\nSales Orders (SO) | Invoices (SI)\nMarketplace (MKT) | WhatsApp (WA)"]
    ORDERS -->|POS Orders tab| POS_TAB["POS Orders section\nFilters: ALL ACTIVE COMPLETED CANCELLED REFUNDS"]

    SALES_TAB -->|SO tab| SO_LIST["Sales Orders list\nSO-YYYY-XXXXX\nDRAFT / PARTIALLY_FULFILLED / CONFIRMED / CANCELLED"]
    SALES_TAB -->|SI tab| SI_LIST["Sales Invoices list\nSI-YYYY-XXXXX\nCONFIRMED"]

    subgraph "Create New Sales Order"
        NEW_SO["/salesorder page\nBreadcrumb: POS / Sales Orders / New\nKeyboard-first: any key opens product search"]
        NEW_SO --> SEARCH_BATCHES["Product search queries product_batches\ndirectly with entity_id filter\nOne result per product (deduped)\nTotal stock aggregated across batches"]
        SEARCH_BATCHES --> SO_ITEMS["Cart table with qty editing\nEnter=edit, Del=remove, ↑↓=navigate"]
        SO_ITEMS --> CUSTOMER["Customer WhatsApp phone (required)"]
        CUSTOMER -->|F5 Place Order| CREATE_SO["POST /api/shop/orders\norder_type = SALES_ORDER\nstatus = DRAFT\nNo stock change at this point"]
        CREATE_SO --> SO_LIST
    end

    SO_LIST -->|Click SO| SO_DETAIL["/pos/orders/[id]\nBreadcrumb: POS / Orders / SO-XXXX\nBack button returns to SO tab"]

    SO_DETAIL -->|F3 or 'Create Sales Invoice' button| SI_OVERLAY["FULL-SCREEN SALES INVOICE OVERLAY\n\nLeft panel:\n- Payment Method (Online/Cash/Credit)\n- Invoice Reference\n- Line status summary (qty/total per line)\n- Keyboard shortcut guide\n\nRight panel:\n- One row per SO line item\n- Batch dropdown (entity batches, FEFO order)\n- Qty input (caps at batch.quantity - used by sibling rows)\n- Unit Price (auto-filled from batch.selling_price)\n- + Batch button for split delivery\n- X to remove extra batch rows\n\nFooter: Subtotal · GST 5% · Total · Create Invoice [F5]\nShortcutBar: ↑↓ Navigate · F5 Create · Esc Cancel"]

    SI_OVERLAY --> VALIDATE{"Sum of sub_batch qty\n= SO line qty\nfor all lines?"}
    VALIDATE -->|Mismatch| WARN["⚠ warning shown\nSubmit button disabled"]
    VALIDATE -->|Match + batch selected| SUBMIT["POST /api/sales/[id]/invoice\n\nServer validates:\n- Remaining qty per line\n  (SO qty − already invoiced)\n- Over-invoice blocked"]

    SUBMIT --> CREATE_SI["SALES_INVOICE created at CONFIRMED\n→ deduct_stock_on_sales_invoice trigger (AFTER INSERT)\n→ SALE inventory_movements per batch\n→ sync_batch_quantity decrements batch.quantity\n→ batch.status = DEPLETED if qty reaches 0"]

    CREATE_SI --> CREDIT_CHECK{payment_method\n= CREDIT?}
    CREDIT_CHECK -->|Yes| KHATA["Khata account created if new\nDEBIT transaction inserted\nOutstanding balance updated"]
    CREDIT_CHECK -->|No| SO_UPDATE
    KHATA --> SO_UPDATE

    SO_UPDATE -->|All lines fully invoiced| CONFIRMED_SO["SO → CONFIRMED\n'All items fully invoiced'"]
    SO_UPDATE -->|Some lines remain| PARTIAL_SO["SO → PARTIALLY_FULFILLED\n'Create another invoice for remaining'"]

    PARTIAL_SO -->|F3 again on SO detail| SI_OVERLAY

    SUBMIT -->|Success| SUCCESS_SCREEN["INVOICE SUCCESS SCREEN\n(replaces overlay form)\n\nGreen confirmation banner\nInvoice number + fulfilment status\nFull printable invoice preview:\n- Vendor details + TPN\n- Customer WhatsApp\n- Line items with batch numbers\n- Subtotal · GST 5% · Total\n- Digital signature\n\n[Download PDF] button (jsPDF + html2canvas)\n[Back to Order] button\nEsc = Back to Order"]

    SUCCESS_SCREEN -->|Back to Order| SO_DETAIL

    SI_LIST -->|Click SI| SI_DETAIL["/pos/orders/[id]\nBreadcrumb: POS / Orders / SI-XXXX\nBack button returns to SI tab"]
    SI_DETAIL -->|F3 or Print Invoice button| PRINT_PDF["PDF download\njsPDF + html2canvas\nSALES INVOICE heading\nGST-compliant format"]
